data.description: BACK ON MARKET! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the heart of Mustang features an open concept living space, a roomy master suite, and a covered back patio. The living area features white painted crown molding, a fireplace, a large dining area, a breakfast bar with wood-look tile accents, can lighting in the kitchen, tons of stained wood cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. The master suite includes a jetted tub, a walk in shower, double vanities, laminate wood flooring, and a large walk-in closet. Other interior features include a vaulted ceiling in the front bedroom, two toned wall in the back bedroom, and cabinets in the utility room. Exterior features include a 2-car garage, large back patio with lights, great landscaping, and guttering. Home is within walking distance to a nearby pond and a city park, and is less than a mile from all the great shopping and dining of Mustang.
